				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Another duergar greets you on the other side of the lake after sailingthere with captain Greymon.\r\n\r\nBoth duergar are surly, but Morghal in particular. She is suspicious of Absolutists, but happy to take their coin. She should be gruff, and absolutely not listless. She tells you that Nere is trapped above."
				}
